# art-src/ — design-time authoring scratch.
#
# Default: ignore large raw working files, but KEEP references and exports
# (they are the design-time source-of-truth a bake traces back to).

# Ignore everything by default...
*

# ...except the things that document and seed a bake-off:
!.gitignore
!README.md
!contact-sheet.html

# Keep per-game/per-sprite folders so the patterns below can reach into them.
!*/
!*/*/

# Committed: the arcade reference frame and any tool/hand exports.
!**/reference.png
!**/*.export.png

# Explicitly drop bulky scratch even if it sneaks into a kept folder.
work/
**/work/
*.psd
*.ase
*.aseprite
*.xcf
*.tiff
